definition: to go/to take/sentence-final interrogative particle/variant of 於|于[yu2]

sentences.english: The results of the isotropic model are better than that of modified Cam-clay.
sentences.chinese: 对比计算结果说明各向同性模型优于修正剑桥模型。

sentences.english: The growth performance of red tilapia cultured in freshwater was superior to other tilapia species.
sentences.chinese: 星洲红鱼在淡水中养殖生长表现优于其他罗非鱼品种。

sentences.english: The operation practice proves that the DDS desulfurizer is clearly better than the tannin extract.
sentences.chinese: 运行实践证明，DDS脱硫效果明显优于栲胶法。

sentences.english: The result showed that tank model surpassed conceptual model of linear reservoirs.
sentences.chinese: 研究结果显示水筒模式整体模拟均优于线性水库。

sentences.english: The cost-effective of the controlled group showed a remarkable advantage over FDC.
sentences.chinese: 对照组药物的成本效果分析优于FDC制剂。

sentences.english: It's obviously that corrosion-resistance and brightness are much better than those of Zn plating.
sentences.chinese: 实验结果表明，其耐蚀性和光亮度明显优于镀锌层。

sentences.english: Inositol hexaphosphate was the main form of organic P in the organic manures and paddy soils.
sentences.chinese: 肌醇六磷酸磷对水稻的营养效果明显优于无机磷。

sentences.english: Docetaxel has demonstrated superiority compared with best supportive care.
sentences.chinese: 多西他赛证明效果优于最好的支持疗法。

sentences.english: The new and trial-manufactured silencer excelled the silencer of original machine on each item of performances.
sentences.chinese: 新试制的消声器各项性能均优于原机消声器。

sentences.english: Attapulgite clay presented better adsorption capability than bentonite.
sentences.chinese: 凹土的吸附脱色性能优于膨润土。

sentences.english: Polyesters exhibit better non-yellowing properties than epoxies, but not as good as aliphatic urethanes.
sentences.chinese: 聚酯的耐黄性优于环氧树脂，但弱于脂肪族聚氨酯。

sentences.english: And it was concluded that the renewable capability of cassava-based ethanol was better than that of gasoline.
sentences.chinese: 得到木薯乙醇燃料可再生性优于汽油的结论。

sentences.english: Therefore DMU is a strategy of product development far superior to existing methods.
sentences.chinese: 因此，DMU是一种远优于现有方法的产品开发策略。

sentences.english: The wind erosion modulus in artificial pasture was less than that in cropland.
sentences.chinese: 人工草地的风蚀模数小于农田，生态效益优于农田。

sentences.english: Relative comparison use tallying surpasses manually tallies.
sentences.chinese: 相对比较使用吻合器优于手工吻合。

sentences.english: On some strains of bacteria, it has better effect in bacteriostasis than Kandfuxin.
sentences.chinese: 该液对多种细菌有抑制作用，其抑菌作用优于康复新。
